Servotronics | Products & Services






























 


716-655-5990☰








				1110 Maple Street
Post Office Box 300
Elma, New York 14059

							716-655-5990							
 






Products & ServicesServotronics’ products and services include single and two-stage servo valves, torque motors, actuators and other motion control components and sub-systems for aerospace platforms, medical devices, and other industrial applications. Our build to print and build to spec manufacturing services provide end-to-end solutions from design engineering and design-for-manufacture through quality testing and global distribution. Servotronics, in partnership with our customers, supports a wide range of platforms including the Boeing 787, Boeing 737 MAX, Boeing 777X, Airbus 320, Airbus A320 NEO, Airbus A350, Airbus A380, F-35 Lightning II, Gulfstream G650, CH-53K Helicopter, and KC-46A Tanker. These programs continue Servotronics’ legacy that includes the early Boeing 700 and Airbus 300 series aircraft, F-14, F-15, F-16, and FA-18 E/F jet fighters, the M1 Abrams tank family, Apache Longbow and Blackhawk helicopters, and other land, sea, and air applications.
   


Products & Services 
Acceptance Testing
Assembly and Calibration
Design Engineering
Fabrication Hardware
Final Inspection
Quality Assurance


