CareersOur Talent Acquisition Mission
Welcome to the Servotronics, Inc. careers page.  We are always looking for dedicated and innovative people to join our team.  Our Human Resource Professionals are committed to sourcing and acquiring the best talent to support Servotronics, Inc. entire operation in meeting its goals through the most valuable resource – its PEOPLE. If you are passionate about being part of a great manufacturing team, we want to hear from you.  
 
Our Culture
We offer a great working environment, learning & development opportunities, and other incentives that support the good health and well-being of our employees. Everyone is focused on creating an atmosphere that fosters teamwork, quality, challenges, fun, safety and cleanliness. 
 
