Quality AssuranceQuality assurance at Servotronics provides a controlled and cost effective program that is consistent with the stringent reliability, traceability and critical performance of our products.
Insuring quality is everyone’s job at Servotronics. The Quality Department is responsible for monitoring piece part and assembly tolerance conformity throughout the manufacturing cycle and for insuring compliance to customer compliance.
Suppliers are selected, monitored and audited for conformity to stringent quality standards.
The quality team uses Three Axis Coordinate Measuring technology as well as Optical Comparitors and other precision high-tech measuring instruments as required.


Products & Services 
Acceptance Testing
Assembly and Calibration
Design Engineering
Fabrication Hardware
Final Inspection
Quality Assurance


