	Code of Ethics



	 


	The Company has adopted
	a Code of Ethics and Business Conduct (the Code) that applies to all directors, officers and employees of the Company as required
	by the listing standards of the NYSE MKT. The Code is available on the Company’s website at www.servotronics.com and the
	Company intends to disclose on this website any amendment to the Code. Waivers under the Code, if any, will be disclosed under
	the rules of the SEC and the NYSE MKT.




	 










